# Inkblot visual language & shell reference

## Motion / layout reference (screen recording)

- **Primary reference**: User screen recording **2026-03-26 ~16:25** (local `.mov` — not in repo). Use it for **timing, weight, and composition** when polishing.
- **Optional captures**: Drop a few representative **PNG/JPEG frames** under `docs/reference/frames/` (create folder when needed) and name them by section (`nav-pill.png`, `scroll-edge.png`, etc.) so assistants can see pixels without video.

When the recording and this doc disagree, **trust the recording for feel** and **update this doc** after changes.

## Global aesthetic

- **Base**: Near-black cinematic UI (`--background` ~`#020617`), high contrast type, restrained chrome.
- **Accents**: Teal / cyan (`#22d3ee`, ice gradients) + soft violet in backlights (`#a78bfa` mixes) — “premium dark mode,” not flat corporate blue.
- **3D / post** (bloom mode): Heavy but tasteful **bloom**, **subtle film grain** (`FilmPass`), **cool grade** — see `engines/citron-bloom/bloom-postprocess/citronBloomComposer.ts`.
- **Typography**: **IBM Plex Mono** for nav pill + mini-player marquee + transport; **Outfit** (primary) + **Fraunces** italic (e.g. “Studio”) for brand wordmark; **Syne** for Citron Bloom **`.scroll-hint`**; story panels use Outfit headings + body (`index.html`).

## Top navigation pill (`index.html` + `src/ui/navChrome.ts`)

- **Shape**: Horizontal **stadium pill** (`.nav-pill-morph`). **Fill**: single semi-transparent **`--nav-glass-fill`** (no accent gradient overlay). **Border**: **one** `1px` edge only — `color-mix(in srgb, var(--border) 50%, transparent)` (half opacity of page `--border`, i.e. 2× more transparent than solid `#1E293B`). **No** duplicate `box-shadow` ring. **Island width** ~`min(78vw, 218px)` desktop / **`min(72vw, 202px)`** narrow; **`--nav-player-w`** = **`calc(var(--nav-island-w) * 0.528)`** (~10% wider strip vs prior 48%). **No** separate `.nav-flora-aura` cluster — flora is **only** the center SVG control.
- **Placement**: Pill stack is **top-right** (`.nav-stack-top-right`, `margin-left: auto`); brand stays **top-left**. No hamburger — WORK / CONTACT always visible.
- **Labels**: **JetBrains Mono** / **IBM Plex Mono**, small caps, wide letter-spacing; ink from `--nav-ink` / `--nav-ink-dim`. **Work / Contact** have **no hover chrome** (no background or glow on `:hover`).
- **Scroll “wind”**: CSS vars `--nav-warp` [0,1], `--nav-dir` ±1 — drive **`perspective(1400px) rotateX translateY skewX scaleX`** on **`.nav-stack-top-right`** from **scroll speed** (`ScrollSystem.velocityPxPerSec`, `updateNavChrome`). Transform origin **top-right** (`100% 0%`). `prefers-reduced-motion` clears the transform.
- **Scene tint (flower journey)**: When **`body.journey-flower-active`**, `--nav-accent` / `--nav-accent-2` track **`--journey-rail`** so **petal gradients** and mini player chrome **follow the act**. Default showcase accent is ice/cyan + violet mix when not on flower journey.
- **Audio**: Toggle is **`#nav-audio-toggle`** wrapping the center flow SVG (`initNavChrome` → `audio.toggleAudio()`). `aria-pressed` synced in `updateNavChrome`.
- **Center audio control (floral)**: Square **`viewBox="0 0 56 56"`** — **six petals** + soft **`nav-floral-core`** heart on **`#nav-deck-rot`** (no vinyl, grooves, tonearm, or outer deck chrome). Rotation: **`updateNavChrome`** integrates angle with **`frameContext.delta`** + smoothed speed. **`--nav-petal-pulse`** drives **`.nav-deck-petals`** and **`.nav-floral-heart`** (brightness). Hit ~**31×31** / mobile **29×29**.
- **Mini player**: **Separate** block **`#nav-player-wrap`**, **only when playing** (`body.music-playing` / `audio-active`): narrower than pill (~**53%** width), **larger vertical gap** from the nav pill, **rounded-rectangle** (~10px radius) with **lighter / more transparent** glass than the pill so it reads as a secondary strip; **opacity** dips when visible, **hover/focus-within** ramps up for control. Transport buttons use **small radius** (~6px), not stadium pills. `⟨⟨` / `⟩⟩`, marquee title from `AudioSystem`; prev/next → `prevTrack` / `nextTrack`.

## Custom scroll thumb (`index.html` + `updateCustomScrollThumb`)

- **Native scrollbars**: Hidden on `html` / `body` (Firefox + WebKit).
- **Placement**: Fixed **right edge**, `z-index: 14`, respects **safe-area**.
- **Divider**: 1px **near-black** vertical line (`.custom-scroll-edge`) — thumb sits **on** the edge axis.
- **Rail**: fixed strip **`~12px`** wide. **Thumb**: ~**8px** wide, **pill** (`border-radius: 999px`), **off-white** (slight slate mix), **min height ~20px**, height ∝ viewport/document ratio (long page → shorter thumb), position from `scrollY / maxScroll`. Fade out when there is nothing to scroll.

## Page shell vs 3D

- **Canvas**: Fixed full-viewport, low z-index; **interaction layer** above for pointer.
- **UI layer**: Mostly `pointer-events: none` with targeted `auto` on interactive nodes.
- **Bloom story copy**: Scroll-synced DOM panels (`#bloom-story`, `--bloom-scroll`); hidden for `?experience=stomp` and non–bloom modes (`body` classes in `inkblotApp.ts`).
- **Bloom scroll cue**: Fixed bottom **`.scroll-hint`** (Citron Bloom only) — **Scroll down** in **Syne** **500**, uppercase, wide tracking; **max opacity 0.7** (times scroll fade from **`--scroll-raw`**); bright ice text + soft cyan glow for legibility.

## Citron Bloom experiences (`engines/citron-bloom/bloom-runtime/`)

- **Registry**: `BloomExperienceRegistry` — add scenes with `register(id, factory)` before bloom component init.
- **Defaults**: `flower` (delicate camera, scroll bloom, optional **dual-scene** transition to `createBloomTransitionScene`) and `stomp` (showcase orbit, iridescent stomp, glass tiles, mist) — `?experience=stomp`.
- **Dual transition**: Distortion + parallax blend in `dualSceneBlendPass.ts`; driven from `inkblotApp.ts` with `smootherstep` on scroll — **only for `flower`**, not stomp.

## Showcase / “Active Theory”–style scene (`bloom-showcase/`)

- **Stomp**: Stacked iridescent tori, `MeshPhysicalMaterial` iridescence + clearcoat.
- **Tiles**: Rounded extruded glass (`transmission`), optional `VideoTexture`, Troika titles; arc placement + `lookAt` center.
- **Mist**: Additive particles purple ↔ cyan (`particleMist.ts`).
- **Camera**: `AnimationSystem` **`showcaseOrbit`** — slow orbit around stomp height with pointer parallax.

## Motion principles

- Prefer **damped** motion (`InkblotCamera`, `ScrollSystem` progress, audio volumes) over snappy unless UI demands it.
- **Scroll velocity** spikes UI reaction (nav warp); **smoothed progress** drives story and bloom.
- Avoid fighting the reference: **one dominant focal point** (flower or stomp), **HUD reads over** the scene without clutter.

